intent: I want to generate original music tracks from text prompts using JavaScript in a web application.
I want to use a Babel plugin to optimize and preprocess my CSS-in-JS styles with Emotion.
I need extra headers and libraries to compile and develop open-source software on my system.
I want to easily add and self-host the Montserrat font in my web project using npm.
